type: BurstDrill
name: Fissure Rig
description: Using entropy as an energy source, creates a miniature fissure to mine resources, including destabilized zircon. In order to resist the rig itself exploding, iron is used for fortification. May optionally be cooled with water.
size: 2
category: production
hardnessDrillMultiplier: 50
